</style><p>然而，这一次，已经证实，以前的观众和艺人粉丝报告称，原本应该结束的Gundo先生的粉丝俱乐部的会员费被收取了。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/yoshiteru73/status/1683709122708140032" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc-zUlI338g4Q6aQcQEgi1YW_6C3GfIVxJnI_yVs3nt_shR3sxQkondU0INz_rhDKwUcnkBXXZ1Yc20BtFvx1t8zkvqL2bbLLzLsT1X-VUY7RY-o8MHaNjHrDjEZq8meZn6lXLcHBCYipw8AeKAIMbo6=w1097-h328-s-no" alt=""/></a></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"> <a href="https://twitter.com/yoshiteru73/status/1683714615484764160" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img data-attachment-id="97755" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-still-collecting-fan-club-dues-for-former-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mirei/anycolor_still_collecting_fan_club_dues_for_former_nijisanji_vtuber_gundo_mirei/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/anycolor_still_collecting_fan_club_dues_for_former_nijisanji_vtuber_gundo_mirei.png" data-orig-size="806,453" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="anycolor_still_collecting_fan_club_dues_for_former_nijisanji_vtuber_gundo_mirei" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/anycolor_still_collecting_fan_club_dues_for_former_nijisanji_vtuber_gundo_mirei.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/anycolor_still_collecting_fan_club_dues_for_former_nijisanji_vtuber_gundo_mirei.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="806" height="453" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content